@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Quy trình Xem Báo Cáo Thống Kê (Quản lý)

actor "Quản lý" as NV
boundary "Giao diện Báo cáo" as UI
participant "ManagerReportController" as Ctrl
participant "ReportService" as ReportSvc
participant "SalaryStatService" as SalarySvc
participant "Repository (DatCho/ChiTiet)" as Repos
database "Database" as DB

NV -> UI : Mở trang Báo cáo\nChọn thời gian (Từ ngày - Đến ngày)\nBấm "Xem Báo cáo"
activate UI

UI -> Ctrl : GET /report/finance?startDate={...}&endDate={...}
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> ReportSvc : getRevenueStats(startDate, endDate)
activate ReportSvc

ReportSvc -> Repos : findSuccessfulBookingsBetween(startDate, endDate)
activate Repos
Repos -> DB : SELECT * FROM DatCho WHERE TrangThai='Thành công' ...
DB --> Repos : return ResultSet
Repos --> ReportSvc : return List<DatCho>
deactivate Repos

ReportSvc -> ReportSvc : Aggregate data (Doanh thu theo ngày/tháng)
ReportSvc --> Ctrl : return RevenueDTO
deactivate ReportSvc

Ctrl -> SalarySvc : getSalaryStats(startDate, endDate)
activate SalarySvc
SalarySvc -> Repos : findCompletedTrips()
activate Repos
Repos --> SalarySvc : List<ChuyenDuLich>
deactivate Repos

SalarySvc -> SalarySvc : Aggregate HDV/TX Salary
SalarySvc --> Ctrl : return SalaryDTO
deactivate SalarySvc

Ctrl -> Ctrl : Build ModelAttributes
Ctrl --> UI : Render View (Thymeleaf/JSON) kèm Dữ liệu Biểu đồ
deactivate Ctrl

UI --> NV : Hiển thị Biểu đồ và Bảng danh sách Cảnh báo báo cáo
deactivate UI

@enduml
